**KMP — two parts**:

1. **LPS array**: For each prefix of needle, longest proper prefix that is also a suffix.
2. **Match scan**: Walk haystack with two pointers; on mismatch, fall back via LPS instead of restarting.

```javascript
function strStr(haystack, needle) {
  if (needle === '') return 0;
  const m = needle.length, n = haystack.length;
  const lps = new Array(m).fill(0);
  for (let i = 1, len = 0; i < m;) {
    if (needle[i] === needle[len]) { lps[i++] = ++len; }
    else if (len) { len = lps[len - 1]; }
    else { lps[i++] = 0; }
  }
  for (let i = 0, j = 0; i < n;) {
    if (haystack[i] === needle[j]) { i++; j++; if (j === m) return i - j; }
    else if (j) j = lps[j - 1];
    else i++;
  }
  return -1;
}
```

**Time**: O(n + m). **Space**: O(m).

